26:51.709 --> 26:55.917
Now, whether it's the art
or the artist, that's yet to say.

26:57.834 --> 26:58.876
We'll know.

27:01.292 --> 27:03.709
But, only after you're sober.

27:12.959 --> 27:14.376
Listen. - What?

27:15.001 --> 27:16.542
You won't work in that bar.

27:17.751 --> 27:19.167
You'll leave that job.

27:20.417 --> 27:21.792
Because I say so.

27:26.417 --> 27:27.834
Do you believe me?

27:35.501 --> 27:36.501
Listen.

27:40.792 --> 27:41.792
What?

27:43.167 --> 27:44.167
Nothing.

27:47.709 --> 27:48.959
Just like that.

28:07.626 --> 28:09.167
Aarohi, are you okay?

28:10.834 --> 28:12.959
Yes. I am fine.

28:21.001 --> 28:22.292
25,000!

28:22.959 --> 28:25.834
That's what I spent
to bring you here.

28:26.459 --> 28:30.084
I suggest,
you pay up and you can leave.

28:33.209 --> 28:34.209
What?

28:34.709 --> 28:35.917
Don't have it.

28:36.542 --> 28:37.584
Go.

28:41.751 --> 28:42.876
Shankar sir.

28:44.959 --> 28:46.584
It's the question of my life.

28:47.209 --> 28:48.626
Please let me go.

28:49.542 --> 28:52.042
I'll return your money
once I get to Mumbai.

28:53.292 --> 28:56.417
No one's going to pay
even 200 for this face.

28:56.959 --> 28:58.084
What do you think?

28:58.167 --> 29:00.376
This is no orphanage.

29:01.167 --> 29:03.042
Pay up and leave.

29:03.501 --> 29:05.376
You take up 50 percent.

29:06.417 --> 29:07.709
And, what are we left with?

29:07.917 --> 29:09.959
We've to buy food
with our own money.

29:10.542 --> 29:13.126
It'll take me months
to arrange that kind of money.

29:13.292 --> 29:14.584
Yeah! Exactly.

29:14.667 --> 29:18.334
That's why you steal
money from the money-bag.

29:18.959 --> 29:20.501
What else do you expect me to do?

29:20.792 --> 29:23.334
You cut 100 rupees
for minor mistakes.

29:23.542 --> 29:25.042
200 for coming late.

29:25.292 --> 29:26.959
And my salary.. - Babu!

29:27.042 --> 29:28.709
What's wrong with her?

29:28.917 --> 29:30.834
She's constantly
saying "I want to go".

29:31.084 --> 29:32.292
She was fine until yesterday.

29:32.751 --> 29:34.626
That singer RJ that
came to bar yesterday..

29:34.709 --> 29:36.251
...Is the one that provoked her.

29:36.334 --> 29:37.542
That he'll make her a singer.

29:37.626 --> 29:39.167
Give her a chance to sing in films.

29:39.501 --> 29:41.084
Since then.. - I see.

29:41.751 --> 29:44.209
RJ. That singer.

29:45.667 --> 29:46.876
Just a minute.

29:48.251 --> 29:49.251
Look.

29:49.459 --> 29:51.667
His picture's in the papers.

29:52.501 --> 29:54.834
He had a fight
with a man yesterday.

29:55.459 --> 29:58.542
He left before the show started.

29:59.126 --> 30:01.959
The organizer of the
show was crying on camera.

30:02.417 --> 30:04.167
There are many other
stories about him.

30:04.417 --> 30:05.792
But, no news about his work.

30:07.876 --> 30:09.834
He'll get you work.

30:11.251 --> 30:15.876
A man that's living off
his hit songs of yesteryear..

30:16.126 --> 30:18.959
...can only pass time with you.

30:19.501 --> 30:20.709
Do you know why?

30:20.876 --> 30:22.959
Because you're worth it.

30:34.626 --> 30:37.834
Hello, sir... you..

30:40.834 --> 30:43.126
I am here for this girl..

30:43.459 --> 30:46.209
...because she's going
to a great singer.

30:47.084 --> 30:50.292
But, I can see her future, not you.

30:52.709 --> 30:53.959
One more thing.

30:55.667 --> 30:56.876
You run a bar.

30:58.042 --> 30:59.542
You live off singers.

31:01.126 --> 31:02.876
Learn to respect singers.

31:04.626 --> 31:06.251
Ones that sing at your bar.

31:07.709 --> 31:10.334
And the ones,
whose songs help you run your bar.

31:11.584 --> 31:12.584
Get that.

31:15.001 --> 31:17.376
Vivek, throw the money on his face.

31:18.501 --> 31:20.834
He isn't worthy of any respect.

31:22.917 --> 31:24.251
Let's go, Aarohi.

31:30.501 --> 31:32.251
Okay. Goodbye.

31:34.376 --> 31:36.001
What's all this, Rahul?

31:37.167 --> 31:38.292
This is it.

31:40.334 --> 31:42.584
I pray to Allah that
you're never heart-broken.

31:42.917 --> 31:44.709
If that happens, don't hesitate.

31:45.001 --> 31:48.709
I'll get you work,
and won't taunt you either.

32:04.709 --> 32:06.126
No, no, it's fine.

32:12.376 --> 32:13.584
I'll drop you.

32:14.876 --> 32:15.876
No.

32:16.084 --> 32:19.876
The place I stay,
isn't your standards.

32:26.167 --> 32:28.084
I've noted my number, address..

32:28.167 --> 32:29.626
...and my manager's
number in your diary.

32:29.709 --> 32:32.792
So, call me when you get a new sim.

32:33.042 --> 32:34.042
Okay-

32:34.292 --> 32:35.417
Don't forget.

32:37.917 --> 32:40.001
Thank you. - For what?

32:40.667 --> 32:42.209
For giving me new hope.

32:44.751 --> 32:46.042
Bye. - Bye,

32:58.626 --> 32:59.626
Listen.

33:00.542 --> 33:01.542
What?

33:02.042 --> 33:03.042
Nothing.

33:06.209 --> 33:07.459
Just like that.

33:32.459 --> 33:34.084
Father!

33:35.626 --> 33:36.626
Aarohi.

33:41.042 --> 33:42.626
You're back. - Yes.

33:44.542 --> 33:46.917
I was thinking about you. - Really?

33:47.251 --> 33:48.667
I even called you in my dreams.

33:50.001 --> 33:51.917
Your mother yelled at me. - Why?

33:52.001 --> 33:55.126
She called me crazy. - Father.

33:58.792 --> 34:01.126
But, you left for three months,
didn't you?

34:01.792 --> 34:05.376
And in one month..
- I'll tell you everything.

34:05.626 --> 34:07.001
But where's mother?

34:07.167 --> 34:08.333
At the station.

34:08.792 --> 34:10.167
Today's Thursday.

34:10.458 --> 34:12.542
She's gone to buy the
Maharashtra Rajya Lottery.

34:13.083 --> 34:15.042
She's been buying lottery
tickets for the past two years.

34:15.126 --> 34:17.626
But she's never won anything
more than 100 rupees.

34:19.083 --> 34:20.251
Enough!

34:21.292 --> 34:23.792
The daughter's back and
the father can't stop yapping.

34:24.042 --> 34:25.042
Mother.

34:29.708 --> 34:31.417
Why didn't you say you're coming?

34:31.792 --> 34:33.751
I would've prepared
something for you.

34:34.251 --> 34:37.542
We live off on fritters.

34:39.542 --> 34:42.626
But now that you're here,
we'll make something nice.

34:43.042 --> 34:46.042
Give me 100 rupees..

34:46.126 --> 34:48.626
...I'll get something
from the market.

34:49.126 --> 34:50.917
We'll make something good today.

34:54.333 --> 34:58.042
Mother, I..

34:59.001 --> 35:01.584
...didn't get paid. - Why?

35:02.501 --> 35:04.126
I met someone.

35:05.292 --> 35:08.584
He said he'll give me a
chance to be a singer, in films.

35:09.751 --> 35:15.542
So I.. - You believed him.
And quit your job.

35:35.917 --> 35:36.917
Mom.

35:39.126 --> 35:40.126
Mom.

35:41.667 --> 35:43.167
Everything will be okay.

35:43.626 --> 35:44.792
Trust..

35:45.709 --> 35:47.376
It's just a matter of few days.

35:47.584 --> 35:50.292
Once I start working.. - So?

35:51.542 --> 35:53.167
I only have 300 rupees.

35:54.042 --> 35:55.167
300 rupees..

35:56.209 --> 35:58.001
Your father doesn't earn a penny.

35:58.542 --> 36:02.376
He.. keeps repairing everyone's
radio and TV's for free.

36:02.584 --> 36:04.584
What are you saying?
- Let me speak.

36:05.167 --> 36:07.542
Is this why I sent
you to the best teachers?

36:09.126 --> 36:10.626
Taught you to speak good Hindi.

36:11.209 --> 36:12.667
So that you can become a great..

36:13.417 --> 36:15.292
I stitched clothes
to pay for your fees.

36:17.251 --> 36:19.959
Finally you found a job,
but you quit that as well.

36:20.584 --> 36:21.584
And..

36:24.459 --> 36:26.292
I don't win.. the jackpot either.

36:28.417 --> 36:29.751
I thought if you get some money..

36:29.834 --> 36:31.417
...I will manage a few months.

36:32.709 --> 36:35.751
Now, I'll have to
borrow from someone.

36:35.834 --> 36:37.084
No, mom.

36:37.542 --> 36:39.209
Let's see whether anyone
will lend me money or not. -Mom.

36:39.292 --> 36:42.792
Mom. Mom. Listen to me. - Aarohi.

36:44.042 --> 36:45.542
Let her go.

36:47.542 --> 36:50.834
Actually, it's not her fault.

36:51.667 --> 36:54.667
She's always seen poverty.

36:55.959 --> 36:58.251
And I never gave
her anything either.

36:58.834 --> 36:59.834
But look.

37:00.917 --> 37:04.417
All our hopes are with you.

37:05.667 --> 37:07.792
We want good things for you.

37:13.126 --> 37:14.126
Father.

37:14.584 --> 37:17.334
First time someone's
believed in me.

37:17.959 --> 37:20.334
First time I believed in someone.

37:20.834 --> 37:24.126
He came all the way from Goa,
only for me.

37:25.876 --> 37:28.501
And he's gone to talk
to someone for me, father.

37:28.709 --> 37:30.334
Uncle, I'm not joking.
- Deadlines, boys.

37:30.417 --> 37:31.417
There's a girl

37:34.292 --> 37:35.334
Thank God!

37:36.001 --> 37:37.251
Get married, straighten up!

37:37.417 --> 37:39.209
No, no, no, it's not that.

37:39.292 --> 37:40.292
No. - No.

37:40.959 --> 37:44.834
This girl's a very,
very, very, very good singer.

37:45.584 --> 37:47.709
I would've believed you
if you had said "very" once.

37:47.792 --> 37:49.251
Please cancel my
appointment for tomorrow.

37:49.501 --> 37:51.084
She was singing in a bar.

37:51.501 --> 37:53.584
Bar.. you mean where
you were obviously..

37:54.709 --> 37:55.709
Yes..

37:56.042 --> 37:57.542
But, what a voice.

37:57.667 --> 37:59.959
I had an entire bottle,
but I couldn't get drunk.

38:00.084 --> 38:01.709
Can you imagine?
- 15 minutes.

38:01.834 --> 38:04.876
Basically, I want you to
give her a chance to sing in films.

38:05.042 --> 38:06.751
Or, make an album.

38:07.542 --> 38:09.376
She's superb, uncle.
I can write that in blood.

38:09.709 --> 38:10.834
Do you have any blood left?

38:11.209 --> 38:12.042
Where is she?

38:12.084 --> 38:13.292
She stays here in Mumbai.

38:14.251 --> 38:15.542
She's from a poor family..

38:15.626 --> 38:18.167
...and performs out of
the city to make a living.

38:18.417 --> 38:19.667
In these small bars.

38:20.084 --> 38:21.917
But I am not going
to let that happen again.

38:22.501 --> 38:23.959
I really want to help her, uncle.

38:24.251 --> 38:25.501
She's a superstar.

38:28.792 --> 38:30.376
Superstar? - Yeah!

38:36.959 --> 38:42.626
A star, is someone whose songs,
and voice..

38:43.709 --> 38:46.917
...makes you want to..
Whistle.

38:48.626 --> 38:49.917
Whistle.

38:50.751 --> 38:53.126
Just like people used
to whistle at your performance.

38:53.209 --> 38:54.584
You were the star. You.

38:54.792 --> 38:56.042
She's better than me.

38:57.167 --> 39:00.042
She's amazing.
I'm telling you, she's amazing.

39:01.584 --> 39:02.584
Call her.

39:04.292 --> 39:06.417
I'll first hear
her and then decide.

39:06.626 --> 39:07.834
You're serious? - Yes.

39:08.459 --> 39:09.459
Yes.

39:11.501 --> 39:13.209
Thank you, uncle.

39:13.792 --> 39:15.542
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

39:15.709 --> 39:17.626
Out. Get out.

39:17.834 --> 39:18.834
Thank you.

39:19.917 --> 39:22.001
Listen to him. He's a good man.

39:26.584 --> 39:29.292
Excuse me, give me a simcard.
- Take this.

39:38.084 --> 39:40.959
You are leaving Deepak's show?

39:43.542 --> 39:45.209
You will forget to sing.

39:55.501 --> 39:57.126
Be careful.
Careful, please.

39:57.251 --> 39:58.251
Careful.

39:59.751 --> 40:01.751
Don't you dare tell
anyone about this!

40:02.042 --> 40:04.751
If any journalist or media-person asks you about him..

40:05.042 --> 40:07.667
...then say,
he's gone to London for a show.

40:08.751 --> 40:12.626
In the meanwhile, nobody comes in,
nobody talks to him.

40:12.751 --> 40:13.917
You get that.

40:21.376 --> 40:22.792
Hello. - Hello.

40:23.501 --> 40:26.126
Can I talk to Mr.
Rahul? My name's Aarohi.

40:26.376 --> 40:28.376
He asked me to call me.

40:28.584 --> 40:31.709
I'm a singer, we met in Goa
and he said.. - Rahul isn't here.

40:32.584 --> 40:34.792
He's gone to London, for his shows.

40:34.917 --> 40:37.667
And he'll return after 20-25 days.
- 20-25 days?

40:39.626 --> 40:41.542
Yes, but just listen to me..

40:42.334 --> 40:44.042
Hello! Hello!

40:52.792 --> 40:58.126
"It's your fault, my heart!"

40:58.626 --> 41:03.917
"it's your fault, my heart!"

41:04.459 --> 41:11.417
"Why did you trust him?"

41:13.042 --> 41:16.876
"All the promises were fake."

41:19.084 --> 41:22.667
"The one you followed here."

41:23.584 --> 41:28.584
"Beloved's nowhere."

41:29.709 --> 41:32.251
"Beloved's nowhere."

41:32.376 --> 41:36.126
"Beloved's nowhere."

41:36.626 --> 41:42.126
"Now, stop seeing those dreams."

41:42.501 --> 41:47.001
"Now, shatter those
dreams yourself."

41:47.042 --> 41:51.917
"Beloved's nowhere."

41:52.042 --> 41:53.584
We don't have evidence..

41:54.501 --> 41:55.792
...whether Deepak's involved or not.

41:56.209 --> 41:58.376
But I swear Rahul.

41:59.334 --> 42:02.584
I will find out whoever he is and..

42:06.209 --> 42:07.792
Did Aarohi call?

42:10.334 --> 42:11.334
Not yet.

42:11.417 --> 42:12.792
Is your phone on?

42:15.876 --> 42:16.876
24/7.

42:26.542 --> 42:28.667
Tell this girl that
it's a wrong number.

42:30.584 --> 42:31.751
Hello. - Hello.

42:31.959 --> 42:33.209
Hello, is Rahul back.

42:33.917 --> 42:34.959
I am sorry, this is a wrong number.

42:35.334 --> 42:36.334
What?

42:36.959 --> 42:38.292
Hello. Hello.

42:39.917 --> 42:50.667
"There's punishment
for every mistake."

42:51.584 --> 42:56.751
"if you're destined for sadness."

42:56.834 --> 43:02.084
"There's always a reason."

43:03.626 --> 43:08.876
"All my pain has
conjured in my tears."

43:09.459 --> 43:14.001
"My tears don't
stop trickling down."

43:14.126 --> 43:16.001
"Beloved's nowhere."

43:16.126 --> 43:19.417
"Beloved's nowhere."

43:20.209 --> 43:23.001
"Beloved's nowhere."

43:23.084 --> 43:25.834
"Beloved's nowhere."

43:29.042 --> 43:31.501
Okay. Give the money.

43:35.459 --> 43:37.626
See you. Goodbye.

43:53.542 --> 43:56.459
This fracture showed
me the importance of my legs.

43:56.667 --> 43:57.751
Take care.

44:01.542 --> 44:02.876
Great.

44:03.251 --> 44:04.251
Good news.

44:04.584 --> 44:06.084
It's time to celebrate.

44:07.001 --> 44:08.792
I'll have a drink with you as well.

44:10.667 --> 44:12.417
Where to? - To look for Aarohi.

44:14.001 --> 44:15.001
Come on.

44:15.209 --> 44:17.584
Excuse me, is this Rahul's house?

44:17.959 --> 44:19.459
Yes, this is his home.

44:19.542 --> 44:21.126
But, sir's out of town.

44:21.209 --> 44:22.959
I don't know when he's coming back.

44:26.542 --> 44:29.542
Vivek sir said he'll be
coming back after 20-25 days.

44:30.459 --> 44:32.042
It's been two months now.

44:32.126 --> 44:33.167
He hasn't returned.

44:33.251 --> 44:34.709
What can I do if he hasn't?

44:34.792 --> 44:36.417
I'll let you know
once he comes back.

44:36.501 --> 44:37.501
Please leave.

44:43.709 --> 44:45.709
Please give this top
Rahul sir when he returns.

44:49.126 --> 44:50.751
Tell him Aarohi was here.

44:51.751 --> 44:53.001
I tried calling him many times.

44:53.167 --> 44:54.751
I'll give it to
him once he returns.

44:54.834 --> 44:56.126
Please go now.

45:27.292 --> 45:29.167
Coming!

45:32.876 --> 45:34.001
What happened?

45:36.834 --> 45:38.042
Sister-in-law, Salim.

45:38.334 --> 45:40.001
Aarohi. What's wrong?

45:41.084 --> 45:42.084
Salim.

45:42.251 --> 45:43.751
What's wrong? Who is it?

45:51.334 --> 45:52.709
What's wrong, Aarohi?

45:53.167 --> 45:54.626
I want a job.

45:57.376 --> 46:01.876
Any place. Good, bad or cheap.

46:02.626 --> 46:03.667
Just get me work.

46:04.292 --> 46:06.501
I need money, Salim.

46:06.959 --> 46:08.459
Come in.

46:12.126 --> 46:14.751
Sir. A girl gave this.

46:17.501 --> 46:18.001
When did she come?

46:18.084 --> 46:19.376
Yesterday evening.

46:19.459 --> 46:21.709
She said she called
you two-three times.

46:21.834 --> 46:23.834
Maybe she spoke to Vivek sir.

46:24.084 --> 46:27.001
She looked decent, so I told you.

46:28.876 --> 46:30.709
Thank you. - Welcome sir.

46:36.084 --> 46:37.667
What the hell is wrong with you?

46:37.834 --> 46:39.417
Don't ask why I did that?

46:39.876 --> 46:40.876
You know.

46:42.001 --> 46:44.917
I told that girl never
to sing in a bar again.

46:45.042 --> 46:47.167
I told her she'll
be a successful singer.

46:47.292 --> 46:49.251
I told her she will be a star.

46:51.542 --> 46:52.959
I went to her hotel, Vivek.

46:53.001 --> 46:54.251
She didn't come to me.

46:54.501 --> 46:55.792
And what did you do?

46:56.126 --> 46:57.542
You humiliated her.

46:57.751 --> 46:59.001
You hid her calls from me.

46:59.959 --> 47:01.001
You lied to her.

47:02.126 --> 47:05.751
You treated her like an enemy.
- Yes, because I'm your friend.

47:06.834 --> 47:08.251
I've been with you for years.

47:08.792 --> 47:10.751
You could've shown
some respect for me.

47:10.959 --> 47:14.084
And for any darn girl..
- She's no ordinary girl!

47:16.167 --> 47:17.667
This is why I did it.

47:18.376 --> 47:19.917
So that you stay away from her.

47:20.959 --> 47:22.667
I didn't want this to happen, man!

47:24.001 --> 47:26.334
First alcohol, then drugs.

47:26.626 --> 47:29.626
And now.. - Whatever I do
with my life is my problem, Vivek.

47:29.751 --> 47:30.251
No!

47:30.334 --> 47:31.876
This isn't your personal problem.

47:31.959 --> 47:33.167
I've been with you for 10 years.

47:33.542 --> 47:35.584
I looked after you, your career.

47:35.834 --> 47:38.001
I saw your success, your downfall.

47:38.292 --> 47:42.126
But, I can't see you
handing over your success..

47:42.292 --> 47:44.376
...which you need the most now,
to some girl.

47:44.959 --> 47:48.042
I can't see you doing
this for someone else instead.

47:48.709 --> 47:51.584
I feel sad. It hurts me.

47:51.834 --> 47:55.042
To know that you've stopped
recognizing your talent.

47:55.876 --> 47:58.626
You've forgotten your own voice.

47:59.042 --> 48:01.042
One that's unmatched.

48:01.584 --> 48:02.584
Why?

48:02.834 --> 48:04.626
Why don't you see yourself?

48:04.876 --> 48:06.709
Why don't you hear yourself?

48:06.959 --> 48:08.584
You call me your enemy.

48:09.792 --> 48:12.917
Just.. look at yourself.

48:15.667 --> 48:16.834
You're right.

48:18.542 --> 48:20.876
But the truth is,
I don't want anything.

48:21.584 --> 48:25.751
Fame, fortune,
success, money, respect.

48:26.209 --> 48:28.792
It should all go to
the one that deserves it.

48:29.751 --> 48:32.001
Give the bread to the
one that's hungry for it.

48:33.001 --> 48:35.792
And I've seen that in that girl.

48:37.251 --> 48:38.834
And I no longer have that.

48:39.709 --> 48:41.084
And I've admitted this truth.

48:41.667 --> 48:42.917
You should too.

48:43.709 --> 48:45.792
Your friend can't pay
you your salary anymore.

48:46.251 --> 48:48.792
RJ. - You're a free man, Vivek.

48:49.751 --> 48:51.709
You can go anywhere you want.

49:05.001 --> 49:06.001
Hello.

49:06.167 --> 49:08.042
Can I talk to Aarohi, please?

49:08.126 --> 49:10.126
She's performing? - Where?

49:10.292 --> 49:11.709
Hotel Nightingale.

49:13.334 --> 49:19.084
"What seemed like reality,
turned out to be an illusion."

49:19.251 --> 49:24.542
"A saga, that was bound
for a twist, has ended."

49:24.709 --> 49:27.251
"I forgot, so did she."

49:27.542 --> 49:33.959
"How do I tell
everyone about this?"

49:34.292 --> 49:39.501
"I've slowly compromised myself."

49:40.042 --> 49:44.626
"I've slowly controlled myself."

49:44.751 --> 49:49.792
"Beloved's nowhere."

49:50.792 --> 49:53.292
"Beloved's nowhere."

49:53.709 --> 49:56.292
"Beloved's nowhere."

49:56.459 --> 50:02.501
"Beloved's nowhere."

50:03.584 --> 50:08.917
"it's your fault, my heart!"

50:09.459 --> 50:14.542
"it's your fault, my heart!"

50:15.209 --> 50:21.626
"Why did you trust him?"

50:23.334 --> 50:24.584
Aarohi! Aarohi!

50:24.792 --> 50:25.667
Please let me explain.

50:25.751 --> 50:28.042
Look. I work here.

50:28.167 --> 50:29.626
Don't create a scene.

50:30.001 --> 50:31.626
I got this job with
great difficulty.

50:31.709 --> 50:33.459
Damn the job,
I want to speak to you.

50:33.584 --> 50:34.792
Why should I?

50:35.501 --> 50:37.209
I've been waiting for two months.

50:37.459 --> 50:40.501
First time I hurt my
parents and trusted someone.

50:40.709 --> 50:42.167
I started dreaming.

50:43.542 --> 50:45.376
Everything seemed true.

50:45.626 --> 50:46.792
What now?

50:48.626 --> 50:49.626
Go ahead.

50:50.584 --> 50:52.542
You can vent all your anger.

50:53.792 --> 50:55.501
I am your culprit.

50:57.709 --> 50:58.917
But, I am not.

51:00.667 --> 51:01.917
I waited for you.

51:02.751 --> 51:04.001
Get in.

51:04.417 --> 51:05.417
Come on. - What are you doing?

51:05.501 --> 51:07.459
Get in. - What are you doing?

51:07.792 --> 51:09.501
What are you doing? - Come on.

51:10.876 --> 51:12.251
I want to tell you a story.

51:15.001 --> 51:17.001
I don't want to hear your story.

51:23.001 --> 51:24.001
Let's go.

51:54.792 --> 51:56.626
If all that happened with you..

51:57.459 --> 51:59.042
...then, why didn't
they show it on TV?

51:59.167 --> 52:00.501
Aarohi, the TV..

52:01.001 --> 52:02.417
Please forget it.

52:02.959 --> 52:04.626
I want to keep my promise.

52:06.251 --> 52:08.251
In fact I brought
Sehgal uncle along.

52:09.001 --> 52:10.584
He's called you at his office.

52:13.334 --> 52:15.251
But, I cannot quit this job.

52:19.959 --> 52:21.334
I cannot take a risk again.

52:21.709 --> 52:22.792
Then don't..

52:23.042 --> 52:25.542
You can keep the job
until you're satisfied.

52:25.834 --> 52:28.251
But, you've believed me so far,
then why not another day.

52:31.709 --> 52:33.376
Be ready at 11 am tomorrow.

52:35.417 --> 52:36.417
Please.

52:39.751 --> 52:40.751
Please!

52:43.542 --> 52:45.001
You sing well, dear.

52:45.667 --> 52:46.667
You're talented.

52:47.126 --> 52:48.667
And you understand tunes.

52:49.126 --> 52:52.084
But, for playback
singing and albums..

52:52.959 --> 52:55.334
...you'll need some grooming.

52:55.792 --> 52:57.001
Just a little.

52:58.334 --> 53:01.334
Because singing in recording
studios with new songs..

53:01.542 --> 53:04.084
...can get a little overwhelming.
- Okay.

53:04.751 --> 53:08.417
Fine.. we'll start your
vocal training from next week.

53:09.167 --> 53:10.126
Yes, I'll do that.

53:10.209 --> 53:12.376
I'll train her. - Fantastic!

53:12.834 --> 53:14.001
What else do you want?

53:21.709 --> 53:23.917
So many awards, records.

53:25.209 --> 53:26.626
They're all yours.

53:27.167 --> 53:30.834
They're mine, or not. I don't know.

53:31.459 --> 53:32.376
What?

53:32.459 --> 53:33.626
Nothing.

53:34.459 --> 53:35.459
Don't worry.

53:35.584 --> 53:38.084
Someday you'll
come with your award.

53:38.584 --> 53:40.001
You'll have more awards than me.

53:40.376 --> 53:41.376
I promise.

53:54.209 --> 53:55.209
What?

53:57.126 --> 53:58.126
Nothing.

54:00.709 --> 54:02.001
Just like that.

54:22.501 --> 54:23.709
I can't do it.

54:24.792 --> 54:26.334
Okay, listen. I will show you.

54:26.501 --> 54:27.751
It's in B flat.

54:29.709 --> 54:36.084
"Just tell me,
whether I want it or not."

54:38.334 --> 54:45.084
"Show me the way to your heart,
whether I want it or not."

54:48.626 --> 54:50.001
You sing so well.

54:51.042 --> 54:53.042
It's your training not me.

54:54.292 --> 54:55.834
Let's start singing.

54:56.501 --> 55:03.709
"Just tell me,
whether I want it or not."

55:05.542 --> 55:12.126
"Show me the way to your heart,
whether I want it or not."

55:14.501 --> 55:22.709
"Let me tell you, that
I don't have faith in my love."

55:23.501 --> 55:25.584
"Still, the heart thought.."

55:25.709 --> 55:32.209
"..now that we're here,
why not ask."

55:32.459 --> 55:38.876
"Just tell me,
whether I want it or not."

55:41.334 --> 55:48.126
"Show me the way to your heart,
whether I want it or not."

56:08.001 --> 56:16.959
"I never had such desires before."

56:17.042 --> 56:25.959
"I never tried this
hard to meet anyone."

56:26.292 --> 56:33.084
"Solve my confusion,
whether I want it or not."

56:35.292 --> 56:42.209
"Express it through your eyes,
whether I want it or not."

56:43.084 --> 56:46.584
Aarohi! Aarohi! Aarohi!

56:49.376 --> 56:50.834
Ladies and Gentlemen.

56:51.126 --> 56:54.126
The time has come,
for me to introduce you all..

56:54.209 --> 56:57.084
...to the nightingale of India,
and our country's..

56:57.167 --> 56:59.084
...latest singing sensation.

56:59.251 --> 57:02.417
The beautiful,
the talented, the wonderful!

57:02.501 --> 57:06.084
Aarohi Keshav Shirke!

57:23.209 --> 57:24.209
Yes, dad.

57:24.334 --> 57:25.876
Rahul. How are you, son?

57:26.626 --> 57:28.959
Everything fine?
- Everything fine, dad.

57:30.001 --> 57:31.459
In fact, I'm really happy.

57:33.084 --> 57:34.292
After a long time.

57:35.001 --> 57:37.084
You're in love, huh!

57:37.334 --> 57:41.667
"Just tell me..

57:43.167 --> 57:44.209
How did you know?

57:44.667 --> 57:46.001
I'm your father.

57:46.959 --> 57:48.126
Come.

57:48.292 --> 57:51.167
When the son's in love,
the father knows.

57:52.084 --> 58:00.167
"Show me the way to your heart,
whether I want it or not."

58:17.334 --> 58:18.126
What happened?

58:18.209 --> 58:20.126
Sir, she needs five more minutes.

58:23.209 --> 58:25.001
It's been half an hour, Rahul.

58:25.626 --> 58:27.834
Is there a problem?
- No, sir. There's no problem.

58:36.917 --> 58:37.917
Aarohi.

58:41.084 --> 58:42.084
Come out.

58:50.542 --> 58:51.542
Let's go.

58:59.084 --> 59:00.959
I cannot sing.

59:03.667 --> 59:05.542
Aarohi, we all get nervous.

59:07.501 --> 59:08.501
I was too.

59:09.751 --> 59:11.209
I ran away from the studio.

59:13.001 --> 59:14.001
It's okay.

59:14.917 --> 59:15.917
No.

59:19.042 --> 59:20.959
The bar was a different story.

59:22.626 --> 59:24.876
Making mistakes were okay.

59:26.334 --> 59:28.917
But, here..
amongst these big people..

59:29.042 --> 59:30.584
You're not alone.

59:32.751 --> 59:33.959
I am with you.

59:37.084 --> 59:38.417
Please, come out.

59:43.167 --> 59:45.042
I cannot sing.

59:54.126 --> 59:55.584
Aarohi, I love you.

59:59.042 --> 01:00:00.084
I love you.

01:00:03.459 --> 01:00:05.292
I've waited too long for this day.

01:00:06.876 --> 01:00:08.042
More than you.

01:00:09.834 --> 01:00:11.834
Come out for me.

01:00:14.459 --> 01:00:15.459
Please.

01:00:36.376 --> 01:00:40.501
"I've small dreams."

01:00:41.126 --> 01:00:45.209
"Dreams have songs."

01:00:45.584 --> 01:00:49.709
"Songs have life."

01:00:50.167 --> 01:00:53.917
"Love and affection."

01:00:54.376 --> 01:00:58.667
"I don't dream any longer."

01:00:59.084 --> 01:01:03.042
"That's without you."

01:01:03.584 --> 01:01:11.667
"I'm finally saying,
what I didn't so far."

01:01:11.959 --> 01:01:20.626
"The heart trusts you,
more than me."

01:01:20.959 --> 01:01:25.251
"I weave dreams about us,
in my empty moments."

01:01:25.459 --> 01:01:29.709
"You're in love with me."

01:01:29.959 --> 01:01:37.834
"I'll never ask you,
whether I want to or not."

01:01:39.001 --> 01:01:47.667
"I want to live in your dreams,
because I want to." - Fantastic.

01:01:49.626 --> 01:01:50.751
Really nice.

01:02:16.667 --> 01:02:18.042
Ladies and Gentlemen.

01:02:18.334 --> 01:02:21.876
Welcome to the Indian Music Awards.

01:02:23.584 --> 01:02:24.584
Finally!

01:02:24.876 --> 01:02:27.917
Uncle. Where's Rahul?
- We're waiting for you.

01:02:29.251 --> 01:02:30.709
When you can't
find Rahul anywhere..

01:02:30.792 --> 01:02:32.626
...you must always check the bar.

01:02:33.376 --> 01:02:36.709
But, it's such a big day
of my life, he should be with me.

01:02:36.792 --> 01:02:38.126
I've been nominated.

01:02:38.209 --> 01:02:39.209
I understand..

01:02:39.417 --> 01:02:40.626
Mom and dad are here.

01:02:40.709 --> 01:02:41.751
<i>I'll</i> just..

01:02:42.042 --> 01:02:44.709
Come. Please come.

01:02:47.001 --> 01:02:49.084
Come on, he'll be here. Come on.

01:02:49.459 --> 01:02:51.459
Please.

01:02:52.667 --> 01:02:54.709
Aarohi! Aarohi!

01:02:57.792 --> 01:02:58.792
Come here.

01:03:00.626 --> 01:03:02.042
Looking for me?

01:03:02.709 --> 01:03:03.917
You scared me.

01:03:04.584 --> 01:03:06.126
Where were you? - Forget that.

01:03:06.209 --> 01:03:07.626
How do you feel?

01:03:08.001 --> 01:03:09.126
It's useless.

01:03:11.501 --> 01:03:13.876
Wonder where you
keep disappearing to?

01:03:15.126 --> 01:03:16.501
I was at the bar.

01:03:17.126 --> 01:03:20.667
If you drink so much, how
will you recognize me in the crowd?

01:03:21.167 --> 01:03:22.167
I will.

01:03:23.917 --> 01:03:28.042
Amongst,
thousands, million, billions.

01:03:29.792 --> 01:03:33.667
I can forget myself, but not you.

01:03:38.626 --> 01:03:40.251
When did you fall so
deeply in love with me?

01:03:40.501 --> 01:03:41.376
Hi, ma'am!

01:03:41.459 --> 01:03:42.792
I'm from CNTV Live.

01:03:42.959 --> 01:03:44.792
Do you mind if I
take a small interview?

01:03:45.542 --> 01:03:46.876
Please. Just for five minutes.

01:03:47.001 --> 01:03:49.542
No, right now I.. - Just a second.

01:03:50.042 --> 01:03:51.251
Never do that.

01:03:51.792 --> 01:03:53.084
Okay. Never do that.

01:03:54.917 --> 01:03:58.126
Go. Time to touch the moon.

01:03:59.834 --> 01:04:00.917
Go get them.

01:04:08.001 --> 01:04:10.917
Ladies and Gentlemen.
Moving on the next award.

01:04:11.584 --> 01:04:13.917
Nidhi Chaudhary for "Aa jara"

01:04:15.584 --> 01:04:16.876
Listen. - Yes, sir.

01:04:17.417 --> 01:04:19.167
Did you get the bottle from home?
- No, sir.

01:04:19.292 --> 01:04:20.709
Then, why are you being a miser?
Pour some more.

01:04:20.792 --> 01:04:21.876
Sorry, sir.

01:04:24.917 --> 01:04:26.542
And award goes to..

01:04:27.792 --> 01:04:29.834
Aarohi Keshav Shirke.

01:04:43.834 --> 01:04:44.834
She won!

01:04:46.084 --> 01:04:47.084
Thank you.

01:04:48.626 --> 01:04:49.959
The girl sings well.

01:04:50.292 --> 01:04:51.292
She's very good.

01:04:51.376 --> 01:04:53.376
I heard she was offered
to sing in films too.

01:04:53.626 --> 01:04:54.917
But she refused.

01:04:55.417 --> 01:04:56.501
She'll say yes.

01:04:56.584 --> 01:04:58.417
Everyone wants to be a star.

01:05:01.792 --> 01:05:04.459
Of course, she will be.

01:05:04.709 --> 01:05:07.709
But, not a star, a maid.

01:05:09.126 --> 01:05:12.001
What's that singer's name?
That star.

01:05:12.084 --> 01:05:13.251
Rahul.

01:05:14.376 --> 01:05:16.376
She'll be his maid.

01:05:17.001 --> 01:05:18.751
And later, his nurse.

01:05:19.501 --> 01:05:21.417
Come on. He loves her.

01:05:22.084 --> 01:05:23.334
He's made her.

01:05:23.667 --> 01:05:26.876
She made it this
far because of him.

01:05:26.959 --> 01:05:29.334
That's what I am
trying to tell you.

01:05:29.834 --> 01:05:33.501
The higher she climbs
the ladder of success..

01:05:33.876 --> 01:05:36.376
...the lower she'll
fall because of Rahul.

01:05:36.792 --> 01:05:39.292
She belongs to a poor family,
after all.

01:05:40.667 --> 01:05:42.959
That's why RJ's taken her in.

01:05:43.417 --> 01:05:46.167
So that he can make her serve him.

01:05:46.792 --> 01:05:50.334
Keep her awake all night,
for his entertainment.

01:05:51.001 --> 01:05:54.501
To vent out the
anger of his failure.

01:05:55.251 --> 01:06:00.709
And as days will go by,
he will start hitting her.

01:06:01.876 --> 01:06:04.626
He'll beat her every day,
humiliate her.

01:06:06.209 --> 01:06:08.251
And once he falls sick..

01:06:08.876 --> 01:06:11.917
...she'll be cleaning his pukes.

01:06:13.292 --> 01:06:14.501
Remember this.

01:06:15.709 --> 01:06:17.834
Often, those who light the lamp..

01:06:18.167 --> 01:06:19.959
...are the ones that douse it later.

01:06:22.001 --> 01:06:26.042
There have been many
such stories in the industry.

01:06:26.459 --> 01:06:28.209
Another glass of whiskey.

01:06:52.376 --> 01:06:53.376
Rahul!

01:06:53.751 --> 01:06:54.751
Rahul!

01:07:05.084 --> 01:07:06.084
Rahul!

01:07:58.334 --> 01:08:01.126
Rahul. What are you doing?
Get down.

01:08:06.876 --> 01:08:09.126
Finally, you touched the moon.

01:08:10.876 --> 01:08:14.417
You were looking very beautiful
on the big screen with the award.

01:08:16.209 --> 01:08:20.417
Does this bottle
look nice in my hands?

01:08:28.959 --> 01:08:30.001
It doesn't.

01:08:33.709 --> 01:08:35.126
But what to do.

01:08:36.459 --> 01:08:38.834
I just can't let go.

01:08:46.251 --> 01:08:50.001
Rahul. - No, no, wait.

01:08:51.209 --> 01:08:53.667
After I got my first
break without any struggle..

01:08:55.667 --> 01:08:59.709
...I got fame, fortune, status.

01:09:01.834 --> 01:09:05.042
The world was at my feet.

01:09:05.876 --> 01:09:07.417
But, I didn't know what to do.

01:09:09.001 --> 01:09:10.667
I couldn't handle the fame..

01:09:12.459 --> 01:09:13.709
...or my senses.

01:09:14.626 --> 01:09:16.376
That was the condition yesterday..

01:09:16.959 --> 01:09:18.834
...It's still the same today.

01:09:19.209 --> 01:09:20.667
And it'll always stay that way.

01:09:20.792 --> 01:09:23.292
Rahul. What are you doing?

01:09:24.834 --> 01:09:26.251
What are you doing?

01:09:26.334 --> 01:09:27.792
Why are you doing this?

01:09:31.042 --> 01:09:33.167
We'll have to end
this relation here.

01:09:35.709 --> 01:09:36.709
Now.

01:09:38.376 --> 01:09:39.751
Nothing's lost yet.

01:09:41.751 --> 01:09:43.459
We aren't so close.

01:09:44.251 --> 01:09:46.042
We can live without each other.

01:09:47.459 --> 01:09:49.042
You're successful now, Aarohi.

01:09:51.167 --> 01:09:52.917
You've everything.

01:09:54.417 --> 01:09:56.292
Go, live your life.

01:09:57.709 --> 01:09:59.167
My habits have scared me.

01:10:02.126 --> 01:10:04.209
I don't know my future.

01:10:05.584 --> 01:10:08.959
What I might turn into.

01:10:09.876 --> 01:10:11.792
How I may treat you.

01:10:13.042 --> 01:10:16.042
It doesn't take long for
one to turn into the devil.

01:10:17.876 --> 01:10:20.001
So, why should I hold you back?

01:10:23.084 --> 01:10:24.376
I can't do this.

01:10:39.834 --> 01:10:42.334
Then.. then..

01:10:43.792 --> 01:10:45.167
Leave this habit.

01:10:46.084 --> 01:10:47.084
Leave it.

01:10:48.292 --> 01:10:49.459
It's no good.

01:10:50.459 --> 01:10:52.001
I'll help you.

01:10:52.209 --> 01:10:53.584
I'll help you leave it.

01:10:53.834 --> 01:10:56.001
Just give me a chance..
- I can never leave it.

01:10:57.501 --> 01:11:01.584
It's like a wife,
that won't ever leave me alone.

01:11:02.959 --> 01:11:04.459
So, listen to me.

01:11:04.876 --> 01:11:06.542
You'll be happier without me.

01:11:08.334 --> 01:11:13.001
That means, you can live
with this habit, but not me.

01:11:15.834 --> 01:11:16.834
Rahul.

01:11:17.251 --> 01:11:20.667
Love is not a joke.
- But my life is.

01:11:22.751 --> 01:11:25.667
But, you always had this habit.

01:11:28.042 --> 01:11:32.042
If you were so scared,
why did you come so close?

01:11:33.459 --> 01:11:35.417
You should've stayed away.
- Exactly.

01:11:36.626 --> 01:11:38.501
Until now, I was my own enemy!

01:11:38.959 --> 01:11:41.626
And before I become a
threat to you, just go away!

01:11:47.126 --> 01:11:48.126
Fine.

01:11:50.126 --> 01:11:51.626
I am going.

01:11:52.959 --> 01:11:56.542
Away, from you and this success.

01:11:57.792 --> 01:12:00.667
Don't misjudge your success.

01:12:02.084 --> 01:12:04.376
Only a few fortune people get it.

01:12:05.251 --> 01:12:06.251
I know.

01:12:07.292 --> 01:12:10.876
And also that,
you were with me in my bad times.

01:12:11.917 --> 01:12:13.834
But if you're not with
me in my good times..

01:12:14.501 --> 01:12:16.126
...then I don't want it.

01:12:36.042 --> 01:12:37.042
Aarohi!

01:12:37.542 --> 01:12:39.459
Aarohi! Aarohi!

01:12:40.042 --> 01:12:41.501
Aarohi, listen!

01:12:45.584 --> 01:12:50.584
"I can't live without you."

01:12:50.751 --> 01:12:55.626
"I don't exist without you."

01:13:00.792 --> 01:13:05.917
"I can't live without you."

01:13:06.042 --> 01:13:10.751
"I don't exist without you."

01:13:11.084 --> 01:13:21.417
"if I separate from you,
I'll lose myself."

01:13:23.459 --> 01:13:28.251
"Because it's you.. it's you."

01:13:28.834 --> 01:13:33.709
"You're my life."

01:13:34.084 --> 01:13:38.501
"My relief, my pain."

01:13:38.792 --> 01:13:44.251
"You're my love."

01:14:04.792 --> 01:14:14.626
"We can't stay away a moment."

01:14:14.959 --> 01:14:19.792
